The paper focuses on evaluating local features for image-based 3D reconstruction, which is a task related to computer vision and graphics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions datasets and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper compares handcrafted and machine learning-based features, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
